# BPERP — Quick reference

## Key paths

| Component | Path |
|-----------|------|
| Backend entry | `backend/server.js` |
| Backend routes (JS) | `backend/routes/*.js` |
| Middleware | `backend/middleware/*.js` |
| Type definitions | `backend/src/types/index.ts` |
| Frontend entry | `frontend/js/app.js` |
| Frontend modules | `frontend/js/modules/*.js` |
| Frontend CSS | `frontend/css/dashboard.css` |
| Electron main | `electron/main.js` |
| Electron preload | `electron/preload.js` |
| Setup wizard | `electron/setup-wizard/` |
| Electron native rebuild | `scripts/rebuild-backend-native.js` |
| Database schemas | `database/*.sql` |
| Build config | `package.json` (build section) |
| Cursor rules | `.cursor/rules/*.mdc` |

## Common commands

```bash
# Development
cd backend && npm run dev          # Backend with nodemon (system Node)
npm run rebuild:backend            # Repo root: native modules for Electron
npm start                          # Electron (forks backend; run rebuild:backend after backend npm install)

# Testing
cd backend && npm test

# Building installers
npx electron-builder --win --publish never
npx electron-builder --linux deb --publish never
npx electron-builder --linux AppImage --publish never

# Database
cd backend && npm run migrate
```
